@SenRubenGallego " Senator" Gallego, I live in Pinal County and your whole lines of crap ring so hollow to our ears.
You're a chameleon that will change his colors at any time to forward his career.
Voter integrity will put you and Sen. Kelly back to the farm.
Adios mì vato!
@SenRubenGallego You are a disgrace to Arizona. When the cheating is proved, you will be in the cell next to your friend Don

@SenRubenGallego He literally broke the law. Stop grandstanding. If he isnt convicted this will spiral into attacks on places of worship for muslims, for jewish and any other religions out there. He broke the law and its one that better be upheld.

@SenRubenGallego I am so happy you are choosing to die on the hill of “invading , terrorizing,intimidating, and humiliating churchgoers is freedom of the press”.   That says everything about you that we need to know.  Going to look great in a campaign ad.
@SenRubenGallego Invading a church service while its going on and scaring all the congregation, pastor and families with kids IS NOT JOURNALISM idiot!  Its a HATE CRIME period.
